Class Donation

  • java.lang.Object
    • problem1.Donation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDonation
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MonthlyDonation, OneTimeDonation, Pledge
    public abstract class Donation
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDonation
    Represents donations made to non-profit organizations, according to their date of donation/pledge as well as the amount given/promised. LocalDateTime uses: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/11/docs/ api/java.base/java/time/LocalDateTime.html Rounding to hundredths place: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/ 11701399/round-up-to-2-decimal-places-in-java
